% Quantified literal (BETA1 spec section 2.3.4).
% Names bound by quantifiers inside the literal are scoped to the
% formula; they do not introduce or shadow logic variables outside.
% The presburger surface uses `exists X, phi` and `forall X, phi`.
% Variables are interpreted over the naturals.
%
% Expected:
%   ?- presburger "exists Y, Y + Y = 6".   => yes.     (Y = 3)
%   ?- presburger "forall Y, Y > 0".       => no.      (Y = 0 counterexample)
